{"tid":1660461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日一定要築人鏈保護清真寺，必要時私了！","createTime":"2019-10-17T13:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T15:12:10.000Z","uid":126782,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e74e59ec7153be5ef886f22f7a94bb8f24ba6b90","tid":1660461,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢幾日風向撚出動得幾頻密大家有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n我可以懷疑警方星期日嘅劇本就係：<br />\n<br />\n遊行中段，派出喬裝黑衣人小隊，向清真寺投擲汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n之後警方就會即刻話，由於有嚴重暴力行為嘅出現，遊行必須中止（正如上次馬集會咁）。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士必須於30分鐘內離開現場，否則將會被視為參與非法集會／暴動。<br />\n<br />\n由於人數眾多，在場嘅和理非一定散唔切，之後就大量人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n同時政府可以開動文宣機器，話黑衣人向清真寺投擲汽油彈，散佈種族仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n一方面合理化清場嘅行為，另一方面都會觸動到美國種族仇恨嘅神經，使人權法係參議院表決前夕增添變數。"},{"pid":"5d05f87187b36388d9d20d42f5d915dbbf4d8c10","tid":1660461,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"22b90f444e570337adcf5e6f277126521e9646b8","tid":1660461,"uid":30865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:48:06.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"8a361df2ad0ee21b7688acd588c8fdb8919fb156","tid":1660461,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58e7c1e6d60e8ba3e44de7e8da6a534fa13a0ea0","tid":1660461,"uid":118311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:48:19.000Z","msg":"中共劇本早已預備，唔好中計"},{"pid":"0dff6eff4fa409fd5bd6822bbdaa67c087db8ca7","tid":1660461,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"f3f774052c0e527ce6af6d5f2500fbe3efe97614","tid":1660461,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"5ff361deea5ba3cc51eac1dc1adbdd54fdf69